				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">They are allocated at link time, just like your own ZP variables, so they will never overlap. You can move and resize the ZP segment if you want just fine.<br /><br />I use a full ZP segment, ie start at 0 and 256 bytes.<br /><br />If you want to see where they end up, see the linker's map file.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

